<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE0143">
<l>kacatapa mutaliya moḻimēṟ ṟōṉṟu</l>
<l>melleḻut tiyaṟkai colliya muṟaiyāṉ</l>
<l>ṅañanama veṉṉu moṟṟā kummē</l>
<l>yaṉṉa marapiṉ moḻi vayiṉāṉa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>And they</l>
<l>since [their] meaning is determined from the context,</l>
<l>are not bound by a particular rule of writing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
